# MagicSquare Project Context

## Project Overview

- Project name: MagicSquare
- Primary language: Python 3.10+
- Goal: ECB architecture and TDD-driven development

## Recommended Structure

```text
src/
  boundary/
  control/
  entity/
tests/
  boundary/
  control/
  entity/
```

## AI Working Behavior

### Before coding

- Review related tests and understand existing test intent first.
- Check for missing test cases mapped to requirements.

### During coding

- Do not generate imports or calls that violate ECB boundaries.
- Do not create functions without type hints.
- Do not implement before confirming RED in TDD flow.

### After coding

- Run changed code and related tests, then verify pass status.
- If TDD rule violations are detected, warn and suggest fixes.
